      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, supported by a precision dual-VANOS variable valve timing system and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous response. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with foresight, including rear subframe reinforcement and a recent comprehensive inspection of the rod bearings and valve lash settings. Suspension geometry remains true, featuring MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup that provides the communicative feedback expected of this platform. While showing signs of consistent use, the drivetrain and structural integrity are excellent, making this an ideal specimen for the purist driver.",
